tagline: A graph analysis plugin for OrbisGIS based on JGraphT
body: GDMS-Topology is a graph analysis plugin for [OrbisGIS](https://github.com/irstv/orbisgis) based on [JGraphT](https://github.com/jgrapht/jgrapht). It is intended for use on transportation networks.
